title: 75 Floral Blocks to Knit
description: A charming collection of square, triangular, diamond-shaped, and hexagonal blocks, all with a floral theme: from traditional blanket squares with petals and rosebuds to colourful blocks with three-dimensional flowers and butterflies, there's something here to inspire every knitter. Great for crafters "on-the-go": it's easy to carry with you just what you need to work a few blocks while travelling, commuting, or meeting friends. When all the blocks are complete, you can assemble the whole project at leisure. Includes: written patterns and corresponding charts; a "Useful Techniques" section for anyone who wants to brush up their knitting skills; "Creative Projects" to help you to make your choice of blocks, yarns, and colours to create your own versions of the projects illustrated.
